1
00:01:39,509 --> 00:01:43,759
[Road to Success]

2
00:01:44,620 --> 00:01:47,820
[Episode 2]

3
00:01:56,039 --> 00:01:57,120
The school's official website is

4
00:01:56,979 --> 00:01:57,320
[Pay attention to mental growth]

5
00:01:57,120 --> 00:01:59,180
full of punishment notices about them.

6
00:01:57,370 --> 00:02:04,620
[School Bulletin Board]

7
00:01:59,430 --> 00:02:02,430
Their grades are basically
at the bottom of the class as well.

8
00:02:02,430 --> 00:02:04,150
No honors,

9
00:02:04,150 --> 00:02:06,230
and no shot at competitions.

10
00:02:07,510 --> 00:02:09,120
It seems that this time,

11
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:11,760
it's really just going to be
a one-round tour for show.

12
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:14,000
Let me just meet them openly.

13
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:26,890
Hello, teacher.

14
00:02:27,110 --> 00:02:29,000
[Fu Xinshu,
former captain of the football team]

15
00:02:27,590 --> 00:02:29,390
Are you the new team supervisor?

16
00:02:29,590 --> 00:02:31,030
Yes, my surname is Lin.

17
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:33,150
Hello, Ms. Lin.

18
00:02:33,590 --> 00:02:34,680
My name is Fu Xinshu.

19
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:36,070
"Ms. Lin"?

20
00:02:36,150 --> 00:02:37,360
I've already told them to hurry up.

21
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:38,360
They should be here soon.

22
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:39,430
I bought you guys some milk tea.

23
00:02:39,430 --> 00:02:40,620
You can distribute it later.

24
00:02:40,620 --> 00:02:42,150
Okay, thank you, Ms. Lin.

25
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:45,520
Fu Xinshu.

26
00:02:47,150 --> 00:02:48,750
Were you also on the football team before?

27
00:02:48,750 --> 00:02:49,560
Yes.

28
00:02:49,890 --> 00:02:50,750
What position?

29
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:52,730
I used to play midfield.

30
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:54,980
"Used to"?

31
00:02:55,010 --> 00:02:56,010
What about now?

32
00:02:58,030 --> 00:03:00,560
I haven't played football
for a long time now.

33
00:03:13,710 --> 00:03:14,710
Wen Chengye!

34
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:16,870
So he's Wen Chengye.

35
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:20,390
[Wen Chengye,
defender of the new football team]

36
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,190
You know me?

37
00:03:20,470 --> 00:03:22,030
You're the transfer student from Class 4.

38
00:03:22,030 --> 00:03:24,560
You and your skateboard are
both very famous.

39
00:04:06,470 --> 00:04:08,270
Ms. Lin, I'll go rush them again.

40
00:04:08,670 --> 00:04:09,670
Hurry up. Come on.

41
00:04:10,150 --> 00:04:11,190
Wen Chengye?

42
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:16,000
What? Are you here for the meeting, too?

43
00:04:16,519 --> 00:04:17,519
Wen Chengye.

44
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:22,000
Please stay for the meeting.

45
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:28,510
-Who does he think he is?
-Who cares about him?

46
00:04:28,510 --> 00:04:30,120
-Just ignore him, Boss.
-Yeah.

47
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:31,120
Teacher?

48
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:33,240
It's you!

49
00:04:36,430 --> 00:04:37,920
There's milk tea!

50
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:38,680
-Teacher,
-How come it's her?

51
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:40,560
you bought the milk tea, didn't you?

52
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:41,560
Come and enjoy it.

53
00:04:41,950 --> 00:04:42,560
Okay!

54
00:04:44,630 --> 00:04:45,690
Boss, here you are.

55
00:04:49,430 --> 00:04:50,920
The teacher even bought us milk tea.

56
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:52,310
She bought us milk tea.

57
00:04:52,310 --> 00:04:54,570
The new teacher is so beautiful and kind.

58
00:04:56,159 --> 00:04:57,870
-Fu!
-There's milk tea for us!

59
00:04:57,870 --> 00:05:00,510
How come you guys arrived
even later than us?

60
00:05:00,510 --> 00:05:02,510
-So what?
-So what, bro?

61
00:05:02,510 --> 00:05:03,720
Feng Suo, the teacher said

62
00:05:03,190 --> 00:05:04,620
[Name: Yu Ming]
[Name: Zheng Feiyang] [Name: Feng Suo]

63
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:05,190
there's no milk tea
for those who are late.

64
00:05:05,190 --> 00:05:07,560
-We will... We will drink it anyway.
-Bro.

65
00:05:06,340 --> 00:05:07,440
[Feng Suo,
former goalkeeper of the football team]

66
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:09,630
Master Zhi Hui was
the last one to get here,

67
00:05:07,610 --> 00:05:07,990
[Zheng Feiyang,
former defender of the football team]

68
00:05:08,010 --> 00:05:08,700
[Zheng Ren, former midfield player
of the football team]]

69
00:05:09,630 --> 00:05:11,120
not me, right?

70
00:05:10,770 --> 00:05:12,230
[Zhi Hui, former midfield player
of the football team]

71
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:13,550
Master,

72
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:15,560
which direction is lucky today?

73
00:05:16,950 --> 00:05:18,390
Anyway,

74
00:05:18,950 --> 00:05:21,120
it's not your position, Zheng Ren.

75
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:23,630
Mr. Zhi Hui,

76
00:05:23,630 --> 00:05:25,430
how about here? How about my position?

77
00:05:25,430 --> 00:05:26,070
Not good, either.

78
00:05:26,070 --> 00:05:27,160
Yours is surely not...

79
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:28,750
It's definitely not your position.

80
00:05:28,750 --> 00:05:29,430
It must be me,

81
00:05:29,430 --> 00:05:29,950
the chosen one.

82
00:05:29,950 --> 00:05:31,190
I'm sure it's not you.

83
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:33,920
There he goes again, the Master.

84
00:05:34,159 --> 00:05:35,159
A one-round tour is guaranteed.

85
00:05:35,159 --> 00:05:35,920
All right, enough.

86
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,520
Here's our team supervisor.

87
00:05:38,190 --> 00:05:40,070
Ms. Lin, everyone is here...

88
00:05:40,630 --> 00:05:41,960
except for Wen Chengye.

89
00:05:45,610 --> 00:05:47,040
Here, I'm announcing something.

90
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:51,040
The school is arranging for you guys
to participate in a football match.

91
00:05:51,270 --> 00:05:53,310
I will serve
as your temporary team supervisor.

92
00:05:53,310 --> 00:05:54,310
My surname is Lin.

93
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:55,600
Football match?

94
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:57,070
At 2:30 PM this Sunday,

95
00:05:57,070 --> 00:05:59,750
let's meet at the school gate to play...

96
00:06:02,950 --> 00:06:04,870
in the Youth Super League qualifiers.

97
00:06:04,870 --> 00:06:06,430
Our rival is Ning'an Experimental School.

98
00:06:06,430 --> 00:06:08,000
Ning'an Experimental School's team is
super strong.

99
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,360
We definitely can't beat them.

100
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,950
How about we forfeit again?

101
00:06:10,950 --> 00:06:12,000
Yeah, let's forfeit.

102
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,730
We haven't trained for 2 years.

103
00:06:13,750 --> 00:06:14,480
What are we going for?

104
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:15,360
Exactly.

105
00:06:15,750 --> 00:06:16,980
To make a fool of ourselves?

106
00:06:16,980 --> 00:06:19,430
Our football team has been disbanded
for so long.

107
00:06:19,430 --> 00:06:21,360
Why are we still playing?

108
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,180
Yeah, why?

109
00:06:22,210 --> 00:06:24,340
-Play for what?
-I'm not going anyway.

110
00:06:24,870 --> 00:06:26,920
They all seem very negative.

111
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:29,700
Those who don't show up will fail PE,

112
00:06:29,870 --> 00:06:30,990
and we'll notify your parents.

113
00:06:30,990 --> 00:06:32,230
I'll take down the names.

114
00:06:32,230 --> 00:06:35,230
Ms. Lin, you probably
don't have that right, I think?

115
00:06:35,260 --> 00:06:37,120
Director Qian gave me this right.

116
00:06:38,420 --> 00:06:39,250
Fu Xinshu,

117
00:06:39,430 --> 00:06:41,159
have everyone sign this later.

118
00:06:45,070 --> 00:06:48,040
Fu, we've already shown you respect.

119
00:06:49,100 --> 00:06:50,050
-Goodbye.
-Bye-bye.

120
00:06:50,050 --> 00:06:50,880
Bye-bye.

121
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:01,960
Ms. Lin,

122
00:07:02,750 --> 00:07:05,000
they don't care about failing,

123
00:07:05,630 --> 00:07:07,890
because they fail almost every subject.

124
00:07:08,430 --> 00:07:10,690
But I'll try my best
to get them all there.

125
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:12,840
Thank you.

126
00:07:16,950 --> 00:07:18,750
Boss, are we really not
playing that match?

127
00:07:17,840 --> 00:07:21,330
[Fight for your youth!]

128
00:07:20,270 --> 00:07:22,190
The team was easily disbanded back then.

129
00:07:22,190 --> 00:07:23,630
Now they want me back?

130
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:25,490
What do they take me for?

131
00:07:25,820 --> 00:07:28,500
That's true, but...

132
00:07:39,870 --> 00:07:41,130
Did you buy this for me?

133
00:07:42,630 --> 00:07:44,290
It definitely wasn't from me.

134
00:07:51,300 --> 00:07:52,070
Could it...

135
00:07:52,630 --> 00:07:54,310
be from Xiaotian?

136
00:07:54,310 --> 00:07:57,510
The Class Beauty wouldn't have
such bad taste, would she?

137
00:08:00,510 --> 00:08:02,070
Bao Xiaotian has good taste,

138
00:08:02,070 --> 00:08:03,630
having taken a liking to you, Boss.

139
00:08:03,630 --> 00:08:05,560
Lin Lu, did you just call me?

140
00:08:10,510 --> 00:08:11,310
Bao Xiaotian,

141
00:08:11,750 --> 00:08:13,280
what do you think of my boss?

142
00:08:29,830 --> 00:08:31,490
I don't know him at all.

143
00:08:35,309 --> 00:08:37,770
There's a second way
to solve this question.

144
00:08:38,630 --> 00:08:40,090
Can you stop being so nosy?

145
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:43,360
Don't you know girls are
easily embarrassed?

146
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:44,630
My bad, my bad.

147
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,080
Open it and see.

148
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:50,530
What do you think

149
00:08:50,690 --> 00:08:51,930
she got me as a gift?

150
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:58,870
Are you sure it's from her?

151
00:08:59,510 --> 00:09:00,710
Why wouldn't it be?

152
00:09:00,790 --> 00:09:02,920
-Do you have a death wish?
-Okay, fine.

153
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:03,940
Chocolate?

154
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:04,750
And a note.

155
00:09:17,900 --> 00:09:18,920
Ms. Lin,

156
00:09:18,940 --> 00:09:20,070
what does this mean?

157
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:22,650
It was definitely you who did this, right?

158
00:09:25,810 --> 00:09:29,220
Do you feel uncertain about your life?

159
00:09:29,250 --> 00:09:31,500
Do you still not know
where your future is heading?

160
00:09:31,500 --> 00:09:33,900
Lin of No. 8 High School
specializes in treating

161
00:09:33,900 --> 00:09:37,430
school refusal, truancy,
lack of motivation, and poor grades.

162
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:45,970
Did you do this, too?

163
00:09:46,550 --> 00:09:48,230
You really love playing pranks, Ms. Lin.

164
00:09:47,810 --> 00:09:48,700
[100 free football equipment rentals]

165
00:09:48,260 --> 00:09:49,140
Childish.

166
00:09:49,170 --> 00:09:51,230
Not only did you give me a little gift,

167
00:09:51,370 --> 00:09:53,150
but you also gave one to Chen Jianghe?

168
00:09:53,150 --> 00:09:54,390
And you, bro.

169
00:09:54,390 --> 00:09:56,240
You actually believed it? You're so naive.

170
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,200
I started working here

171
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:59,800
this Monday, September 2nd,
for the first day.

172
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:01,600
You registered last week,

173
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:02,730
before I even got here.

174
00:10:02,730 --> 00:10:03,530
Furthermore,

175
00:10:04,960 --> 00:10:06,160
where did you find it?

176
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:08,170
In my desk drawer.

177
00:10:08,170 --> 00:10:10,370
Then tell me, my dear student, Qin Ao.

178
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:12,010
In broad daylight,

179
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:13,360
how did I go hide this chocolate

180
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:15,560
in your desk drawer without being seen?

181
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:18,080
It was computer class this morning.

182
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:20,210
So you could sneak into the classroom.

183
00:10:20,510 --> 00:10:22,240
Besides, you just look like a student.

184
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:23,150
Thank you.

185
00:10:23,150 --> 00:10:24,510
But I'm not into that.

186
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:26,300
I

187
00:10:26,370 --> 00:10:28,510
graduated with a master's degree
from Yongchuan University.

188
00:10:28,510 --> 00:10:30,280
I was our province's top liberal arts scorer
in the college entrance exam.

189
00:10:30,280 --> 00:10:32,510
I have published 6 SCI papers in total—

190
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:34,170
4 as the first author.

191
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:36,350
I've received first-class scholarships
for 7 years.

192
00:10:36,350 --> 00:10:38,880
If I hadn't wanted to live a life
of just getting by,

193
00:10:38,880 --> 00:10:41,010
why would I have ended up sitting here?

194
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:42,230
Ms. Lin,

195
00:10:42,330 --> 00:10:44,930
isn't it inappropriate for you
to brag so much?

196
00:10:45,030 --> 00:10:46,720
Ms. Lin, was it really not you?

197
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:54,930
Then why is your phone number on it?

198
00:10:55,550 --> 00:10:56,790
It also asks us to come to you.

199
00:10:56,790 --> 00:10:57,720
It must have something to do with you.

200
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:58,690
Think it over again, Ms. Lin.

201
00:10:58,690 --> 00:11:00,950
Boss, let's go over there to check it out.

202
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:06,120
There's a note
in every piece of chocolate.

203
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:07,600
What are these? I don't understand.

204
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:09,330
Nine of them have words on them.

205
00:11:09,750 --> 00:11:11,410
Why doesn't this one have any?

206
00:11:15,850 --> 00:11:16,850
How should I know?

207
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,480
Ms. Lin,

208
00:11:20,870 --> 00:11:22,360
aren't you a master's graduate

209
00:11:22,360 --> 00:11:24,360
from Yongchuan University,

210
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:26,550
the province's top liberal arts scorer
in the college entrance exam,

211
00:11:26,550 --> 00:11:28,080
and a straight-A student who wrote

212
00:11:28,080 --> 00:11:30,690
some SOS papers?

213
00:11:30,870 --> 00:11:31,910
You should know, right?

214
00:11:31,910 --> 00:11:33,840
It's "SCI."

215
00:11:34,510 --> 00:11:35,960
I know.

216
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:40,040
The straight-A student
can't even solve this?

217
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:44,510
If I can't solve a puzzle,

218
00:11:44,510 --> 00:11:46,710
there could only be two possibilities.

219
00:11:46,910 --> 00:11:49,720
Firstly, it's not a puzzle at all.

220
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:52,200
Secondly, I don't
want to solve it for now.

221
00:11:55,640 --> 00:11:57,210
Each sentence has a different length.

222
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:57,090
[100 free football equipment rentals]

223
00:11:57,240 --> 00:11:58,870
There is a repeated word.

224
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:01,750
Is it a crossword puzzle?

225
00:12:02,580 --> 00:12:03,440
[Diligence makes up for a lack of talent]
[Hard work makes the door to success]

226
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:04,360
Okay.

227
00:12:05,390 --> 00:12:07,320
The grid for puzzle solving.

228
00:12:07,670 --> 00:12:08,390
Got it.

229
00:12:07,970 --> 00:12:10,320
[Hints about the poems]

230
00:12:12,390 --> 00:12:13,540
[Diligence makes up for a lack of talent]
[Hard work makes the door to success]

231
00:12:15,880 --> 00:12:17,030
Ms. Lin,

232
00:12:17,050 --> 00:12:18,810
have you found anything?

233
00:12:19,250 --> 00:12:20,800
[Make a great coup]

234
00:12:25,300 --> 00:12:27,510
[Start over again] [Dreams come true]

235
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:34,790
"Xin-shu."

236
00:12:32,960 --> 00:12:35,440
[Stay calm] [Dreams come true]

237
00:12:37,110 --> 00:12:38,370
Which word do you think

238
00:12:39,930 --> 00:12:41,650
should be filled in the front?

239
00:12:41,680 --> 00:12:43,250
Isn't that self-evident?

240
00:12:43,720 --> 00:12:44,670
It must be...

241
00:12:45,040 --> 00:12:45,840
-"Fu."
-"Fu."

242
00:12:51,590 --> 00:12:52,790
What brings you here?

243
00:12:55,060 --> 00:12:55,940
Hello, Ms. Lin.

244
00:12:57,270 --> 00:12:58,090
What's up?

245
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:02,080
Did you guys change your mind

246
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:03,360
and decide to play
in the match this weekend?

247
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:04,390
No way!

248
00:13:04,390 --> 00:13:06,150
Bro, it's daytime.

249
00:13:06,150 --> 00:13:07,080
Wake up, please.

250
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:08,790
I don't play meaningless matches.

251
00:13:08,790 --> 00:13:09,920
We can't win anyway.

252
00:13:10,870 --> 00:13:11,720
I know.

253
00:13:13,390 --> 00:13:14,030
But what if I

254
00:13:14,030 --> 00:13:15,830
still want to invite you to play?

255
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:17,490
Let's get down to business.

256
00:13:18,360 --> 00:13:19,960
Someone played a prank on me.

257
00:13:22,320 --> 00:13:22,960
Simply put,

258
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:24,550
someone gave us a puzzle,

259
00:13:24,550 --> 00:13:26,030
a crossword puzzle.

260
00:13:26,030 --> 00:13:28,720
And this is our deduction process.

261
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:31,000
We've deduced
that your name goes in this blank.

262
00:13:29,680 --> 00:13:31,370
[Start over again] [Make a great coup]

263
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:35,600
-"Xinshu."
-You are the one related

264
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:37,290
to Ms. Lin and us.

265
00:13:37,310 --> 00:13:38,550
So the answer must be you.

266
00:13:38,550 --> 00:13:39,600
Why me?

267
00:13:39,600 --> 00:13:40,320
Even though he's

268
00:13:40,320 --> 00:13:42,630
-the one who wants to play the most...
-We also inferred it from this hint...

269
00:13:42,630 --> 00:13:43,790
Did you receive anything similar?

270
00:13:43,790 --> 00:13:45,870
Judging from his reaction,

271
00:13:46,820 --> 00:13:48,440
he didn't do this.

272
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:51,540
My brain hurts.

273
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:54,080
Let's go. Time to go home for dinner.

274
00:13:54,610 --> 00:13:55,780
I remember now.

275
00:13:58,000 --> 00:13:59,080
I did receive something.

276
00:13:59,080 --> 00:13:59,960
Really?

277
00:14:00,410 --> 00:14:01,290
What is it?

278
00:14:04,360 --> 00:14:06,200
I'll tell you if you come to play

279
00:14:06,480 --> 00:14:07,550
in the match this weekend.

280
00:14:07,550 --> 00:14:08,200
Hold on.

281
00:14:09,890 --> 00:14:11,320
You're still one player short

282
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:12,790
for the team, right?

283
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:15,000
I'll handle it.

284
00:14:23,270 --> 00:14:25,690
[Hongjing No. 8 High School]

285
00:14:25,780 --> 00:14:30,150
[Administrative Building]

286
00:14:34,870 --> 00:14:37,390
I don't know how to do the homework
the teacher assigned last time.

287
00:14:37,390 --> 00:14:40,120
Same here.
I've been looking it up for a long time.

288
00:14:51,270 --> 00:14:52,130
Wen Chengye...

289
00:14:56,030 --> 00:14:56,960
What do you want from me?

290
00:14:56,960 --> 00:14:57,790
Just say it.

291
00:14:59,030 --> 00:14:59,840
You left early today,

292
00:14:59,840 --> 00:15:00,870
so you didn't hear it.

293
00:15:00,870 --> 00:15:02,000
This Sunday afternoon at 2:30,

294
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:03,510
we'll meet at the school gate
for the match.

295
00:15:03,510 --> 00:15:04,440
Can you join us?

296
00:15:08,940 --> 00:15:10,400
You've waited for so long.

297
00:15:10,440 --> 00:15:11,920
Is this very important to you?

298
00:15:11,920 --> 00:15:12,850
Very important.

299
00:15:13,390 --> 00:15:14,910
Ever since the team disbanded,

300
00:15:14,910 --> 00:15:16,030
what I want to do most is

301
00:15:16,030 --> 00:15:18,430
to play football with everyone once again.

302
00:15:19,240 --> 00:15:21,770
I also hope you can join us
as our new teammate.

303
00:15:30,510 --> 00:15:31,390
Okay.

304
00:15:31,790 --> 00:15:32,920
I will definitely go

305
00:15:33,120 --> 00:15:34,180
and arrive on time.

306
00:15:58,840 --> 00:15:59,960
The lights are off?

307
00:16:16,120 --> 00:16:17,390
So he is home.

308
00:16:18,840 --> 00:16:19,750
No way,

309
00:16:19,750 --> 00:16:21,240
is he bathing in the dark?

310
00:16:21,640 --> 00:16:23,700
Or did he forget to turn off the water?

311
00:16:34,780 --> 00:16:36,620
This guy is too weird.

312
00:16:45,370 --> 00:16:46,330
Hello,

313
00:16:46,750 --> 00:16:47,550
I'd like to know

314
00:16:47,550 --> 00:16:49,510
about the new tenant upstairs.

315
00:16:51,720 --> 00:16:53,600
I know he pays a lot of rent,

316
00:16:53,600 --> 00:16:54,600
but I still need to know

317
00:16:54,600 --> 00:16:56,330
his basic information, right?

318
00:16:58,000 --> 00:16:59,200
If he's really that rich,

319
00:16:59,200 --> 00:17:00,840
why didn't he rent a luxury apartment?

320
00:17:00,840 --> 00:17:04,119
Just because he's handsome
doesn't mean he's a good person.

321
00:17:04,119 --> 00:17:05,790
Come on, sir.

322
00:17:05,790 --> 00:17:07,869
Just think it over.
I'm not joking with you.

323
00:17:07,869 --> 00:17:09,109
Installing a bathtub in the living room

324
00:17:09,109 --> 00:17:10,310
of this old residential building

325
00:17:10,310 --> 00:17:11,349
and bathing in the dark—

326
00:17:11,349 --> 00:17:12,829
don't you think it's so weird?

327
00:17:12,829 --> 00:17:15,270
What if he's some psycho killer?

328
00:17:15,270 --> 00:17:18,400
Think about how dangerous it is
for me to live here alone.

329
00:17:20,400 --> 00:17:21,109
Okay.

330
00:17:21,790 --> 00:17:24,990
Please make sure
you investigate this thoroughly for me.

331
00:17:41,200 --> 00:17:42,350
You're still up now?

332
00:17:43,860 --> 00:17:45,290
It's only 9 o'clock.

333
00:17:49,240 --> 00:17:50,550
Um,

334
00:17:51,030 --> 00:17:53,230
since when have you been standing here?

335
00:17:54,210 --> 00:17:54,970
Not long ago.

336
00:17:56,200 --> 00:17:58,460
Just since you started making that call.

337
00:18:04,480 --> 00:18:05,400
That's great.

338
00:18:07,270 --> 00:18:09,440
I'm used to sleeping early
and waking up early.

339
00:18:09,440 --> 00:18:11,790
Then I'll get in now.

340
00:18:11,790 --> 00:18:14,000
I am 30 years old,

341
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:15,960
from Yongchuan, unemployed.

342
00:18:20,570 --> 00:18:21,350
Good night,

343
00:18:21,910 --> 00:18:22,910
Miss Landlady.

344
00:18:24,590 --> 00:18:26,550
I don't want to kill you yet.

345
00:18:39,000 --> 00:18:41,060
I've only been at work for 2 days,

346
00:18:41,240 --> 00:18:43,570
and I've already received 2 little gifts.

347
00:18:45,640 --> 00:18:47,150
A football lending card.

348
00:18:47,350 --> 00:18:48,860
A little note.

349
00:18:49,880 --> 00:18:53,410
I was also asked to rebuild
the football team as the supervisor.

350
00:18:55,160 --> 00:18:57,480
Who on earth is messing with me,

351
00:18:58,070 --> 00:18:59,750
and why?

352
00:19:05,790 --> 00:19:08,060
And the QR Code upstairs

353
00:19:08,680 --> 00:19:10,350
is also weird.

354
00:19:17,480 --> 00:19:19,720
Is there any connection

355
00:19:20,350 --> 00:19:22,400
between them?

356
00:19:32,640 --> 00:19:34,350
Do you have any idea?

357
00:19:52,750 --> 00:19:54,210
Out for a morning workout?

358
00:19:55,810 --> 00:19:57,240
You got the pancakes from this restaurant?

359
00:19:57,240 --> 00:19:58,770
The line is usually super long.

360
00:19:58,770 --> 00:20:00,100
They are freshly baked.

361
00:20:00,110 --> 00:20:00,790
Try some?

362
00:20:01,930 --> 00:20:03,790
No, thanks. I have a match to go to.

363
00:20:18,920 --> 00:20:21,050
We still don't have everyone here yet.

364
00:20:21,550 --> 00:20:22,310
Come on...

365
00:20:23,440 --> 00:20:25,750
Even though I don't want to play,
I still arrived early.

366
00:20:25,750 --> 00:20:28,200
In view of this pre-match gathering alone,

367
00:20:28,300 --> 00:20:30,360
you can already tell today's match is

368
00:20:30,550 --> 00:20:31,410
looking rough.

369
00:20:34,330 --> 00:20:35,980
Are you giving up already?

370
00:20:36,480 --> 00:20:38,590
What? We're obviously going to lose.

371
00:20:38,960 --> 00:20:40,390
Watch your mouth.

372
00:20:40,760 --> 00:20:41,840
I'm in the team.

373
00:20:42,070 --> 00:20:45,530
I once dribbled past 5 players in a row
and scored with one kick.

374
00:20:46,000 --> 00:20:46,880
And now?

375
00:20:47,350 --> 00:20:48,510
You pant after running 2 laps.

376
00:20:48,510 --> 00:20:50,270
A true hero doesn't boast of past glory.

377
00:20:50,270 --> 00:20:52,340
-I mean, I can still do it now, okay?
-Keep bragging.

378
00:20:52,340 --> 00:20:54,730
Ms. Lin, is there no milk tea today?

379
00:21:01,090 --> 00:21:02,400
Is everyone here?

380
00:21:10,030 --> 00:21:11,230
Where's Wen Chengye?

381
00:21:11,360 --> 00:21:14,030
[Everyone else is here
and waiting for you.Are you almost here?]

382
00:21:13,600 --> 00:21:14,400
Fu!

383
00:21:14,920 --> 00:21:17,350
Are you sure
Wen Chengye promised to come today?

384
00:21:17,350 --> 00:21:19,350
Is he too scared of losing to show up?

385
00:21:24,160 --> 00:21:26,550
"I'm not coming, you idiot"?

386
00:21:24,820 --> 00:21:25,860
[I'm not coming, you idiot.]

387
00:21:28,950 --> 00:21:30,390
It's fine, Fu.

388
00:21:30,550 --> 00:21:32,160
I... I'll get revenge for you later.

389
00:21:32,160 --> 00:21:33,310
Great.

390
00:21:33,310 --> 00:21:35,590
Ms. Lin, since Wen Chengye isn't coming,

391
00:21:35,590 --> 00:21:36,830
we don't even have enough players.

392
00:21:36,830 --> 00:21:38,560
Let's just disband right here.

393
00:21:43,680 --> 00:21:46,280
You've got a point.
I'll go tell Director Qian.

394
00:21:46,660 --> 00:21:48,310
It's time!
Why haven't you gotten on the bus?

395
00:21:48,310 --> 00:21:49,110
The match is about to start!

396
00:21:49,110 --> 00:21:50,590
Director Qian, here's the thing.

397
00:21:50,590 --> 00:21:52,640
Wen Chengye got held up
and couldn't make it.

398
00:21:52,640 --> 00:21:54,240
The team is one player short.

399
00:21:54,750 --> 00:21:57,350
Can we just not go?

400
00:21:57,350 --> 00:21:59,580
If he's not coming,
we'll find someone else!

401
00:21:59,580 --> 00:22:01,030
What do you mean by "not go"?

402
00:22:01,030 --> 00:22:03,440
The school leaders are
taking this very seriously today.

403
00:22:03,440 --> 00:22:05,200
How can you just forfeit easily?

404
00:22:05,200 --> 00:22:06,350
But we don't have enough players.

405
00:22:06,350 --> 00:22:08,350
Then let's figure it out!

406
00:22:09,400 --> 00:22:10,590
Don't pull a long face.

407
00:22:10,590 --> 00:22:11,920
It's my treat today!

408
00:22:11,920 --> 00:22:13,450
Come on, have some goodies.

409
00:22:13,590 --> 00:22:15,510
Don't pull a long face. Give me a smile.

410
00:22:15,510 --> 00:22:17,110
I bought some snacks for you.

411
00:22:17,110 --> 00:22:18,440
You're usually so cute.

412
00:22:19,720 --> 00:22:20,780
Don't look so down.

413
00:22:22,030 --> 00:22:24,160
You usually have the brightest smile.

414
00:22:24,240 --> 00:22:25,440
Come on, here you are.

415
00:22:25,440 --> 00:22:26,830
Come on, come on!

416
00:22:26,830 --> 00:22:28,090
-Thank you, Director.
-Thank you, Director.

417
00:22:28,090 --> 00:22:30,620
-Thank you, Director.
-Thank you, Director.

418
00:22:31,310 --> 00:22:32,790
Thank you, Director.

419
00:22:34,510 --> 00:22:35,370
Here's for you.

420
00:22:36,310 --> 00:22:38,180
Don't worry, just go ahead.

421
00:22:38,240 --> 00:22:40,000
Leave this matter to me.

422
00:22:40,000 --> 00:22:42,350
I promise before you even arrive,

423
00:22:42,350 --> 00:22:45,350
the substitute will already be
waiting there for you.

424
00:22:45,480 --> 00:22:46,400
Take it.

425
00:22:47,210 --> 00:22:47,670
Get in the bus!

426
00:22:47,670 --> 00:22:48,410
Thank you.

427
00:22:48,440 --> 00:22:49,510
Hurry up! Stop dawdling!

428
00:22:49,510 --> 00:22:50,590
Stop messing around. Hurry!

429
00:22:50,590 --> 00:22:51,550
It's getting late!

430
00:22:51,550 --> 00:22:53,980
Go! Get moving! Get on the bus!

431
00:22:54,010 --> 00:22:55,400
Hurry up! Come on!

432
00:22:55,400 --> 00:22:56,590
Get on! Get on now!

433
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:23,550
This bus is pretty fancy.

434
00:23:24,920 --> 00:23:26,400
And they're well-equipped.

435
00:23:26,400 --> 00:23:27,680
I'm so jealous.

436
00:23:28,440 --> 00:23:30,200
-Thank you, Coach.
-Thank you, Coach.

437
00:23:30,200 --> 00:23:31,330
-Hurry up!
-Come on!

438
00:23:31,550 --> 00:23:33,510
Their conditions are way too good.

439
00:23:34,110 --> 00:23:35,310
That's a bit too much.

440
00:23:35,720 --> 00:23:36,590
They're so delicate.

441
00:23:36,590 --> 00:23:37,270
Hurry up.

442
00:23:38,880 --> 00:23:39,810
Let me take this.

443
00:23:41,550 --> 00:23:43,410
Boss, I want this treatment, too.

444
00:23:45,160 --> 00:23:47,030
Then you should ask Ms. Lin for it.

445
00:23:48,030 --> 00:23:49,510
What supplies do we have?

446
00:23:51,280 --> 00:23:52,350
I ordered some water for you

447
00:23:52,350 --> 00:23:53,720
from a nearby farmhouse.

448
00:23:53,720 --> 00:23:54,450
Oh, God...

449
00:23:54,470 --> 00:23:56,440
Let's go.

450
00:23:56,440 --> 00:23:57,270
Here we are.

451
00:23:57,270 --> 00:23:58,200
Come on, get off.

452
00:23:58,790 --> 00:24:00,790
Relax and play well.

453
00:24:00,790 --> 00:24:01,880
-Okay!
-Okay.

454
00:24:02,350 --> 00:24:04,680
When did we get another football team?

455
00:24:05,240 --> 00:24:07,030
They came for the chemistry competition,

456
00:24:07,030 --> 00:24:08,590
taking the test
in the building over there.

457
00:24:08,590 --> 00:24:09,350
Chemistry has always been

458
00:24:09,350 --> 00:24:12,080
Hongjing's strongest subject
in competitions.

459
00:24:13,270 --> 00:24:14,160
I'm coming!

460
00:24:14,160 --> 00:24:16,510
Chen Weidong
from the track and field team?

461
00:24:16,510 --> 00:24:17,830
I came right after Director Qian

462
00:24:17,830 --> 00:24:18,640
talked to me.

463
00:24:18,640 --> 00:24:20,400
So everyone's here. Let's go.

464
00:24:20,640 --> 00:24:21,840
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

465
00:24:24,570 --> 00:24:29,170
[Yongchuan Provincial Youth Super League]

466
00:24:28,760 --> 00:24:29,640
Stop there.

467
00:24:29,190 --> 00:24:33,610
[Hongjing No. 8 High School vs.
Ning'an Experimental School]

468
00:24:31,790 --> 00:24:33,830
Everyone, show your faces.

469
00:24:33,830 --> 00:24:36,510
Why bother taking photos
if it's going to be a one-round tour?

470
00:24:36,510 --> 00:24:38,000
She was probably
just completing a photo task

471
00:24:38,000 --> 00:24:39,530
assigned by Director Qian.

472
00:24:42,030 --> 00:24:43,270
Ms. Lin,

473
00:24:43,270 --> 00:24:44,270
can I really do it?

474
00:24:44,790 --> 00:24:45,680
Chen Weidong,

475
00:24:45,680 --> 00:24:46,680
we never thought about winning.

476
00:24:46,680 --> 00:24:48,400
Why are you taking it so seriously?

477
00:24:48,400 --> 00:24:50,160
Bro, Wen Chengye didn't come,

478
00:24:50,160 --> 00:24:51,240
but you did.

479
00:24:51,240 --> 00:24:52,710
You have my respect.

480
00:24:55,030 --> 00:24:56,400
Ning'an united,

481
00:24:56,400 --> 00:24:58,460
fighting only for the championship!

482
00:25:02,590 --> 00:25:05,680
Should we also come up
with a slogan together?

483
00:25:06,550 --> 00:25:08,150
What's there to think about?

484
00:25:08,160 --> 00:25:10,160
We're just here to run a few laps,

485
00:25:10,160 --> 00:25:12,110
lose the game, and put on a show.

486
00:25:12,110 --> 00:25:14,110
Then we have to put on a full show.

487
00:25:14,830 --> 00:25:15,640
Come on.

488
00:25:16,110 --> 00:25:17,710
Who can come up with a slogan?

489
00:25:18,350 --> 00:25:19,880
Qi Liang, let Qi Liang do it.

490
00:25:20,550 --> 00:25:21,350
Why don't you do it?

491
00:25:21,350 --> 00:25:23,010
Aren't you always talkative?

492
00:25:24,350 --> 00:25:25,810
Then I'll come up with one.

493
00:25:27,790 --> 00:25:30,400
Hongjing, Hongjing, shining stars!

494
00:25:31,510 --> 00:25:33,510
-That's so tacky.
-Oh...

495
00:25:37,550 --> 00:25:38,750
Then you think of one.

496
00:25:42,310 --> 00:25:43,200
Gather here.

497
00:25:43,200 --> 00:25:46,200
If you don't join me,
I'll tell Director Qian about it.

498
00:25:46,680 --> 00:25:47,790
There you go again,

499
00:25:47,790 --> 00:25:49,310
bringing up Director Qian.

500
00:25:49,310 --> 00:25:50,110
Come on.

501
00:25:51,920 --> 00:25:52,680
Director Qian.

502
00:25:52,680 --> 00:25:55,640
Hongjing, Hongjing, shining stars!

503
00:25:55,640 --> 00:25:58,440
-Hongjing, Hongjing...
-Hongjing, Hongjing...

504
00:25:59,110 --> 00:26:00,400
Say it louder.

505
00:26:01,510 --> 00:26:03,400
-Hongjing, Hongjing,
-Hongjing, Hongjing,

506
00:26:03,400 --> 00:26:05,350
-shining stars!
-shining stars!

507
00:26:08,200 --> 00:26:09,240
Let's go.

508
00:26:16,060 --> 00:26:17,440
Today's match is about to start.

509
00:26:16,340 --> 00:26:16,720
[Yongchuan Provincial Youth Super League]

510
00:26:16,740 --> 00:26:17,270
[Hongjing No. 8 High School vs.
Ning'an Experimental School]

511
00:26:17,440 --> 00:26:18,400
The two teams are

512
00:26:18,400 --> 00:26:20,510
Ning'an Experimental School
and Hongjing No. 8 High School.

513
00:26:20,510 --> 00:26:21,750
The match officially begins.

514
00:26:21,750 --> 00:26:24,310
First up, there's a coin toss
to choose sides.

515
00:26:24,310 --> 00:26:27,000
The ones in blue and black striped uniforms
are from Ning'an Experimental School.

516
00:26:27,000 --> 00:26:28,720
Their team is extremely fast

517
00:26:28,720 --> 00:26:29,720
and known as the "Cheetahs."

518
00:26:29,720 --> 00:26:32,440
The team in the blue jerseys is
Hongjing No. 8 High School.

519
00:26:32,440 --> 00:26:34,960
They haven't participated
in any match for 2 years.

520
00:26:34,960 --> 00:26:36,310
In fact, just 2 months without playing

521
00:26:36,310 --> 00:26:37,750
can completely change a team.

522
00:26:37,750 --> 00:26:40,160
And they've been absent for 2 whole years.

523
00:26:40,160 --> 00:26:40,920
In the football fans' eyes,

524
00:26:40,920 --> 00:26:42,750
their chances of winning look slim.

525
00:26:42,750 --> 00:26:44,160
The 2 forwards
of Hongjing No. 8 High School

526
00:26:44,160 --> 00:26:45,550
are No. 9, Qin Ao,

527
00:26:45,550 --> 00:26:47,200
and No. 7, Chen Jianghe.

528
00:26:47,200 --> 00:26:47,790
Chen Jianghe is

529
00:26:47,790 --> 00:26:50,160
good at one-touch finishing in the box.

530
00:26:50,160 --> 00:26:50,830
As for Qin Ao,

531
00:26:50,830 --> 00:26:52,440
he's good at using changes of pace

532
00:26:52,440 --> 00:26:54,300
to pull off one-on-one dribbles.

533
00:26:54,920 --> 00:26:56,510
This is
Hongjing No. 8 High School's goalkeeper,

534
00:26:56,510 --> 00:26:57,400
No. 1, Feng Suo.

535
00:26:57,400 --> 00:26:59,920
He is the team's last line of defense.

536
00:26:59,920 --> 00:27:01,240
Hongjing's 2 core defenders

537
00:27:01,240 --> 00:27:03,400
are No. 6, Lin Lu, and No. 5, Yu Ming.

538
00:27:03,400 --> 00:27:04,920
Because of his small stature, Lin Lu was

539
00:27:04,920 --> 00:27:05,790
once jokingly called

540
00:27:05,790 --> 00:27:08,070
a player who'd jump up
and shatter your knees.

541
00:27:08,070 --> 00:27:09,200
Next to him is Yu Ming,

542
00:27:09,200 --> 00:27:10,880
capable of charging down the flanks.

543
00:27:10,880 --> 00:27:13,110
The 2 teams are making
their final pre-match preparations.

544
00:27:13,110 --> 00:27:14,030
I wonder if it's because the ones

545
00:27:14,030 --> 00:27:14,960
from Hongjing No. 8 High School

546
00:27:14,960 --> 00:27:16,160
haven't played for so long,

547
00:27:16,160 --> 00:27:17,350
but they look a bit loose.

548
00:27:17,350 --> 00:27:18,510
QR Code?

549
00:27:20,400 --> 00:27:21,640
What is he doing here?

550
00:27:24,070 --> 00:27:25,160
Come on! Go for it!

551
00:27:26,160 --> 00:27:27,160
Mark your men

552
00:27:27,510 --> 00:27:28,710
and watch the timing!

553
00:27:29,070 --> 00:27:30,000
Come on!

554
00:27:32,790 --> 00:27:34,070
The match begins!

555
00:27:34,070 --> 00:27:35,200
Ning'an Experimental School's team
kicks off.

556
00:27:35,200 --> 00:27:36,750
Their passing speed is very fast.

557
00:27:36,750 --> 00:27:38,750
Hongjing No. 8 High School
stands no chance

558
00:27:38,750 --> 00:27:39,960
