-Mark him!

561
00:27:43,680 --> 00:27:45,550
No. 10 Fu Xinshu,
is like Hongjing's midfield engine.

562
00:27:45,550 --> 00:27:47,070
He commands the team's defense

563
00:27:47,070 --> 00:27:49,830
