of the entire Hongjing Team.

564
00:27:50,160 --> 00:27:52,110
I didn't expect to be
this fun participating

565
00:27:52,110 --> 00:27:53,720
in such a high school league.

566
00:27:54,310 --> 00:27:56,370
These kids aren't entirely useless.

567
00:27:58,340 --> 00:28:00,050
It's so passionate!

568
00:28:00,110 --> 00:28:02,000
This is their true battlefield.

569
00:28:02,550 --> 00:28:03,720
I suddenly feel that

570
00:28:03,720 --> 00:28:05,160
