571
00:28:05,160 --> 00:28:06,160
Shoot!

572
00:28:08,720 --> 00:28:11,110
So fast? Has it even been a minute?

573
00:28:12,030 --> 00:28:13,440
They can't be this bad, right?

574
00:28:12,350 --> 00:28:14,700
[Ning'an Experimental School 01]
[Hongjing No. 8 High School 00]

575
00:28:16,680 --> 00:28:18,030
Goal! One to zero.

576
00:28:18,030 --> 00:28:19,790
Ning'an Experimental School
scored the first goal.

577
00:28:19,790 --> 00:28:21,400
The Hongjing No. 8 High School's players

578
00:28:21,400 --> 00:28:22,880
look nowhere near as good as before.

579
00:28:22,880 --> 00:28:24,350
During the 2 years they haven't competed,

580
00:28:24,350 --> 00:28:26,400
did they do nothing but sleep?

581
00:28:26,400 --> 00:28:27,720
Hongjing No. 8 High School is
in very poor form.

582
00:28:27,720 --> 00:28:28,790
After the goal,

583
00:28:28,790 --> 00:28:31,270
