seem to have started blaming each other.

584
00:28:31,270 --> 00:28:33,880
No. 9 Qin Ao and No. 6 Lin Lu
miscommunicated.

585
00:28:33,880 --> 00:28:34,750
Yeah,

586
00:28:34,750 --> 00:28:35,880
there's still time!

587
00:28:35,880 --> 00:28:37,510
Go for it!

588
00:28:37,510 --> 00:28:39,350
-Captain Fu Xinshu is passing the ball.
-Watch the ball!

589
00:28:39,350 --> 00:28:40,920
But the ball has been intercepted!

590
00:28:40,920 --> 00:28:42,030
The ball!

591
00:28:43,790 --> 00:28:45,200
Ning'an shoots!

592
00:28:45,200 --> 00:28:47,270
The ball was saved by Feng Suo!

593
00:28:51,880 --> 00:28:54,590
The ball is once again
with Hongjing No. 8 High School.

594
00:28:54,590 --> 00:28:56,640
Number 9, Qin Ao,
with his individual skill,

595
00:28:56,640 --> 00:28:58,400
