into the penalty area.

596
00:28:58,400 --> 00:28:59,510
Shoot!

597
00:29:00,030 --> 00:29:03,000
Unfortunately, it was also saved
by Ning'an's goalkeeper.

598
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:04,480
Both sides have exchanged
attacks and defenses,

599
00:29:04,480 --> 00:29:06,740
neither gaining an absolute advantage.

600
00:29:07,030 --> 00:29:08,270
The running speed of both teams' players

601
00:29:08,270 --> 00:29:10,160
has noticeably slowed down on the field.

602
00:29:10,160 --> 00:29:10,830
Lack of endurance

603
00:29:10,830 --> 00:29:12,830
has always been Ning'an's weakness.

604
00:29:12,830 --> 00:29:15,960
However, Hongjing Team has clearly
lacked training for 2 years,

605
00:29:15,960 --> 00:29:18,420
and their stamina is also
failing to keep up.

606
00:29:26,110 --> 00:29:27,640
Why is he still here?

607
00:29:28,380 --> 00:29:30,050
Could it be that he

608
00:29:30,080 --> 00:29:32,280
also likes watching football matches?

609
00:29:38,210 --> 00:29:39,870
You know about football, too?

610
00:29:41,350 --> 00:29:42,110
A little bit.

611
00:29:43,510 --> 00:29:44,370
Watch the game.

612
00:29:46,830 --> 00:29:49,550
Hongjing's No. 10 is advancing
at high speed with the ball.

613
00:29:49,550 --> 00:29:52,110
The 2 players collided for the ball,
and the ball was intercepted!

614
00:29:52,110 --> 00:29:52,830
They crashed into each other.

615
00:29:52,830 --> 00:29:54,000
Fu Xinshu was knocked down,

616
00:29:54,000 --> 00:29:55,730
falling heavily to the ground.

617
00:29:57,550 --> 00:29:58,510
The right side!

618
00:29:59,070 --> 00:30:02,720
