dribbled past Hongjing's No. 5, Yu Ming.

619
00:30:03,200 --> 00:30:05,110
He's still advancing.

620
00:30:07,790 --> 00:30:09,880
Hongjing Team's No. 12
used his body to block,

621
00:30:09,880 --> 00:30:11,310
but the referee blew the whistle!

622
00:30:11,310 --> 00:30:13,480
-Looks like No. 12 committed a handball!
-Calm down, calm down.

623
00:30:13,480 --> 00:30:15,480
It was my shoulder that hit the ball.

624
00:30:18,030 --> 00:30:19,090
What's happening?

625
00:30:19,270 --> 00:30:20,160
The referee thinks

626
00:30:20,160 --> 00:30:21,510
your defending player

627
00:30:21,510 --> 00:30:23,440
opened his arms
in the opponent's penalty area,

628
00:30:23,440 --> 00:30:24,830
and his arm touched the ball,

629
00:30:24,830 --> 00:30:25,830
so a penalty kick was awarded.

630
00:30:25,830 --> 00:30:27,750
So did he actually commit a handball?

631
00:30:27,750 --> 00:30:29,350
From my angle,

632
00:30:29,380 --> 00:30:30,080
