639
00:30:46,240 --> 00:30:47,780
The first lesson for me?

640
00:30:47,810 --> 00:30:49,170
So pretentious.

641
00:30:50,310 --> 00:30:51,030
Never mind.

642
00:30:51,310 --> 00:30:52,960
We're just
going through the motions anyway.

643
00:30:52,960 --> 00:30:54,200
The referee has finally ruled

644
00:30:54,200 --> 00:30:56,200
