646
00:30:57,960 --> 00:31:00,240
Possession goes back to Ning'an.

647
00:31:02,000 --> 00:31:04,750
Next is a tense penalty kick.

648
00:31:05,830 --> 00:31:07,200
Ning'an Team's No. 14 is

649
00:31:07,200 --> 00:31:08,860
